            &lt;td style="width: 68.4707%; vertical-align: top;"&gt;
            &lt;div data-empty="true"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
            The BNP Paribas Group&amp;rsquo;s Morocco subsidiary BMCI also responds to the Vigeo Eiris questionnaire in accordance with its scope and businesses. In 2016, BMCI&amp;rsquo;s laudable performance secured the bank a listing in the &lt;strong&gt;EURONEXT-Vigeo Eiris Ranking Emerging 70&lt;/strong&gt; index.
